<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="id">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Plenger NFT Project</title>
  <style>
    body {
      margin: 0;
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      background: #0f172a;
      color: white;
    }
    header {
      padding: 20px;
      text-align: center;
      background: #020617;
    }
    header h1 {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 2.5rem;
      color: #38bdf8;
    }
    nav {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      gap: 20px;
      margin-top: 10px;
    }
    nav a {
      color: white;
      text-decoration: none;
    }
    section {
      padding: 60px 20px;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .hero {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1e293b, #0f172a);
    }
    .btn {
      background: #38bdf8;
      padding: 10px 20px;
      border-radius: 10px;
      text-decoration: none;
      color: black;
      font-weight: bold;
    }
    .grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr));
      gap: 20px;
      margin-top: 30px;
    }
    .card {
      background: #1e293b;
      padding: 20px;
      border-radius: 15px;
    }
    footer {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 20px;
      background: #020617;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

<header>
  <h1>Plenger NFT</h1>
  <nav>
    <a href="#about">About</a>
    <a href="#collection">Collection</a>
    <a href="#roadmap">Roadmap</a>
    <a href="#contact">Contact</a>
  </nav>
</header>

<section class="hero">
  <h2>Welcome to Plenger NFT</h2>
  <p>Proyek NFT unik dengan karakter khas dan utilitas Web3 masa depan.</p>
  <a href="#collection" class="btn">Explore Collection</a>
</section>

<section id="about">
  <h2>About Project</h2>
  <p>Plenger NFT adalah koleksi digital eksklusif yang dibangun di blockchain dengan tujuan memberikan nilai nyata kepada holder melalui utilitas dan komunitas.</p>
</section>

<section id="collection">
  <h2>Collection</h2>
  <div class="grid">
    <div class="card">NFT #001</div>
    <div class="card">NFT #002</div>
    <div class="card">NFT #003</div>
    <div class="card">NFT #004</div>
  </div>
</section>

<section id="roadmap">
  <h2>Roadmap</h2>
  <p>Phase 1: Launch Collection</p>
  <p>Phase 2: Community Growth</p>
  <p>Phase 3: Utility Development</p>
  <p>Phase 4: Metaverse Integration</p>
</section>

<section id="contact">
  <h2>Contact</h2>
  <p>Twitter: @plengerNFT</p>
  <p>Discord: Coming Soon</p>
</section>

<footer>
  <p>© 2026 Plenger NFT Project</p>
</footer>

</body>
</html>
